name: Painter Panda - KuD-037
description: He held in captive since birth. looking at the visitor through his cage in zoo everyday make him bored until he found what interesting to him. He found colors in mud and leaf paste, he likes how it can be mixed and produce different results. He try to make some shape someday and enlightened. From that day, he start to paint something with the paint his caretaker gave him.
